The paper is about detecting malware using machine learning and deep learning, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The use of machine learning and deep learning algorithms for malware detection suggests that the paper could also be categorized under machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also discusses the unique challenges and open research problems in the domain, which could suggest a software engineering (cs.SE) aspect. Finally, the use of deep learning models suggests that the paper could also be categorized under neural networks (cs.NE).
